{"tid":678334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普確認放生「中興」, 引起共和黨和民主黨的議員不滿","createTime":"2018-05-26T03:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T02:43:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"39d7022bedf5a5195898cf4bab1d67d0d9a08f67","tid":678334,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.hkcnews.com/article/12392/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-12393/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%A4%A9%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%85%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%BB%A0%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-%E5%BC%95%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%85%A9%E9%BB%A8%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F12392%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581-%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0-12393%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2588%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2585%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2588%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2a8e5787\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcnews.com/article/12392/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-12393/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E5%9B%9E%E5%A4%A9%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%85%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%BB%A0%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-%E5%BC%95%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%85%A9%E9%BB%A8%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF</a></span><br />\n<br />\n眾聞<br />\n【中興回天】特朗普允美廠與中興交易 引共和民主兩黨不滿<br />\n撰文: 記者陳駿豪 | 發佈日期: 26.05.18 | 最後更新: | 2018-05-26 11:38:57<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》引述知情人士稱，特朗普政府已知會國會議員，華府與中國第二大電訊設備商中興達成協議，原本被美國封殺的中興現存一線生機。該知情人士透露，特朗普此舉希望為日後與中國磋商貿易問題時，消除談判障礙。不過，特朗普的做法，引起議員不滿。<br />\n<br />\n由於美國商務部從中協商，中興仍要繳付巨額罰款，以及聘請按美國法規執法的官員到中興廠房。另外，中興對美國商務部承諾，撤換現時的管理層。《紐約時報》引述該知情人士稱，由於中興向美國商務部妥協，商務部會撤消「拒買令」，讓中興得以購買美國製造的產品。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特朗普周五晚在Twitter確認有關消息</strong>，並斥奧巴馬政府和民主黨領袖、紐約州資深聯邦參議員舒默（Chuck Schumer）「任意容讓中興電訊公司在無安全監管的情況下坐大。」他又指，奧巴馬政府只會與伊朗做蝕本生意。他說，「我拆去重來，再開放市場，現在電訊產品都有高級別的安全保證，中興的管理層和董事會一定要撤換，一定要買美國零件和繳付13億美元（約101億港元）罰款。」<br />\n<br />\n今次協議容許中興電訊再次與美國公司做生意，包括無線電通訊科技公司高通（Qualcomm）。高通位於聖地牙哥的廠房，為中興電訊供應晶片（即芯片）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>放生中興    引共和民主兩黨合攻<br />\n<br />\n特朗普今次放生中興，引起兩黨議員不滿。民主黨資深參議員舒默和共和黨佛羅里達州參議員魯比奧，均要求華府不要向中興讓步。不少兩黨議員都認為，「中興事件」牽涉國定安全和執法問題。</strong><br />\n<br />\n民主黨馬里蘭州參議員范荷倫表示，「中興電訊代表對美國的威脅，目前華府所訂的協議，根本無法回應（有關國家安全）的基本事實。」他續稱，「若果特朗普總統不將我們的安全置於中國就業情況之前，議員會合兩黨之力，阻止他如此舉動。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中興被美國封殺，直接阻礙美中兩國的經貿談判。報道稱，中國國家主席習近平以個人名義，希望特朗普能下令重新檢視對中興的決策。特朗普此舉引起多名國家安全興問和兩黨議員不滿。</strong><br />\n<br />\n位列中國第二大電訊廠商的中興通訊，上月被美國商務部以中興沒有履行與美國和解協定中的部分協議為由，禁止美國企業7年內向中興銷售軟硬件和技術晶片。商務部的調查報告指，中興違反美國制裁禁令，自2010年1月至2016年4月期間，分別向伊朗及北韓出售美國產品及科技。中興與美國去年就事件達成和解協議，同意美國提出的7年出口特權禁令，並向美國賠償約8.9億美元（約69億港元）、解僱4名高層，以及懲戒公司35名員工。然而，美國商務部稱，中興在2016年及2017年向美方作出錯誤陳述，沒有執行和解協議，且未處分涉事的35名員工，決定封殺中興。"},{"pid":"890031bc3382831379bc0742b10d4e52387b7ac5","tid":678334,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://gizmodo.com/trump-announces-plan-to-save-zte-after-his-administrati-1826341271\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2Ftrump-announces-plan-to-save-zte-after-his-administrati-1826341271&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ce730ae8\" target=\"_blank\">http://gizmodo.com/trump-announces-plan-to-save-zte-after-his-administrati-1826341271</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDonald J. Trump<br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n Senator Schumer and Obama Administration let phone company ZTE flourish with no security checks. I closed it down then let it reopen with high level security guarantees, change of management and board, must purchase U.S. parts and pay a $1.3 Billion fine. Dems do nothing....<br />\n7:07 AM - May 26, 2018<br />\n<br />\nDonald J. Trump<br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n ...but complain and obstruct. They made only bad deals (Iran) and their so-called Trade Deals are the laughing stock of the world!<br />\n7:13 AM - May 26, 2018<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMarco Rubio<br />\n@marcorubio<br />\n Yes they have a deal in mind. It is a great deal... for #ZTE &amp; China. #China crushes U.S. companies with no mercy &amp; they use these telecomm companies to spy &amp; steal from us. Many hoped this time would be different. Now congress will need to act.  <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/25/us/politics/trump-trade-zte.html?smprod=nytcore-ipad&amp;smid=nytcore-ipad-share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-trade-zte.html%3Fsmprod%3Dnytcore-ipad%26smid%3Dnytcore-ipad-share&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6dce85d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/25/us/politics/trump-trade-zte.html?smprod=nytcore-ipad&amp;smid=nytcore-ipad-share</a> &hellip;<br />\n12:39 AM - May 26, 2018<br />\n<br />\nChuck Schumer<br />\n@SenSchumer<br />\n If the administration goes through with this reported deal, President Trump would be helping make China great again.  Would be a huge victory for President Xi, and a dramatic retreat by Pres Trump. Both parties in Congress should come together to stop this deal in its tracks. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nytimes/status/1000065729050349568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes%2Fstatus%2F1000065729050349568&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2ef9de9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes%2Fstatus%2F1000065729050349568&h=221f7654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nytimes/status/1000065729050349568</a> &hellip;<br />\n1:46 AM - May 26, 2018"},{"pid":"2138c94cb0a37fce351b5d1533a77dc059ed5bfd","tid":678334,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"使唔使過國會？"},{"pid":"4ffb3ac4972810ce9054736006a7809c92d2da11","tid":678334,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"大龍鳳做個樣比棋王刁睇下姐"},{"pid":"4c4265d036a99087ef10df77d9948f45aa960dfb","tid":678334,"uid":89931,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"打倒特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c99292ad98c37bdd90c640aa015d3f48f21e4ce","tid":678334,"uid":16493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"點呀又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689c937af056f7e136faf85739beea8b1fdf2e4b","tid":678334,"uid":69885,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"但放生咗嘅ZTE，仲喺本身嗰間咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac283850ca1210f19af18ee5e50e478b570d9eb2","tid":678334,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"689c937af056f7e136faf85739beea8b1fdf2e4b","tid":678334,"uid":69885,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"但放生咗嘅ZTE，仲喺本身嗰間咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"幕後話事人一樣無變 - 習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10aa40d16b28be8b9f1c860bb381ef18fa8b9db","tid":678334,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04: